@subsection super


Gets the content of the block from the parent template. You can pass the name of the block of the parent block you want to access. If no name is passed, then the current block’s parent is used.

Sample usage:

@example
@{% super "stylesheets" %@}

@{% block stylesheets %@}
  @{% super %@}
@{% endblock %@}
@end example

