@c punctuation (opening parens), and ``urlize`` will still do the right thing.
@c 
@c Links generated by ``urlize`` have a ``rel="nofollow"`` attribute added
@c to them.
@c 
@c For example::
@c 
@c     {{ value|urlize }}
@c 
